# Perceptron from Scratch ðŸš€

This project is an **end-to-end implementation of the Perceptron algorithm** from scratch using Python and NumPy â€” without using any high-level ML libraries. It includes training logic, prediction, model serialization, automated testing, CI/CD integration via GitHub Actions, and deployment as a PyPI package.

